calamares-settings-foundry-linux (1.0.3) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Add Theme-API=2.0 and QtVersion=6 to SDDM metadata.desktop — SDDM 0.21
    requires these fields to load a theme; without them it falls back to the
    built-in gray greeter. Fix sddm.login() session arg: pass 0 (int) not
    sessionModel.index(0,0) (QModelIndex).

 -- Will Norris <wbnorris@gmail.com>  Fri, 23 May 2026 15:00:00 +0700

calamares-settings-foundry-linux (1.0.2) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Fix SDDM Main.qml: use Qt6-style unversioned imports and drop
    SddmComponents import entirely — sddm/userModel/sessionModel are SDDM
    context properties, no module import required. Qt5-versioned imports
    cause silent parse failure on Ubuntu 26.04 Qt6.

 -- Will Norris <wbnorris@gmail.com>  Sat, 23 May 2026 12:30:00 +0700

